REWORK E COMMERCE UBIN by AlexzCorp

Database Structure
    1. Users Table for
                    -> Login Page
                    -> Registration Page
                    -> Testimonial Page
        Table Structure 
            1. Id_user
            2. Email
            3. Name
                -> first name
                -> last name
            4. Telephone
            5. Password
            6. Level
                -> super_admin
                -> admin
                -> member


    2. Products Table for
                        -> Review Product Page
                        -> Checkout Page / Order Page
                        -> Payment Page
        Table Structure
            1. Id_product
            2. Name
            3. Price
            4. Weight
            5. Description
    

    3. Orders Table for 
                        -> Checkut Page / Order Page
        Table Structure
            1. Id_order
            2. Id_user
            3. Id_product
            4. Time
            5. Status
                -> unpaid
                -> paid
        


Component:
    1. Home Page
        -> Top Discount Product
        -> Free Shipping Product
        -> Top 10 Product
        -> Testimonial about Product
        -> About Website
            -> Contact
            -> Social Media
        
    2. Review Product Page
        -> Huge Image Product (zoom features only)
        -> Price
        -> Description about Product
        -> Add to cart BUTTON
        -> Form Comment/Testimoni about product

    3. Login Page
        -> Website logo
        -> Form for Login

    4. Registration Page
        -> Website Logo
        -> Form for Registration
        -> Confirmation with email

    5. Checkout Page / Order Page
        -> Product
        -> Price
    6. Payment Page
